  "name": "Deck Legacy",
  "type": "deck",
  "description": "<p>This Path represents the many ways in which your character’s story could begin. What peoples and places do they hail from? What traditions and customs started shaping them from the very start? What framework or cultures did they grow up with that still influences them today? A person can become who they are because of or despite their origins. When choosing from these fragments, keep this in mind and decide not only what influences were there at the start but how those factors impacted your character and what unique choices they made in the face of them.</p>",
